data.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Age greater than or equal to 18 years;
* Acceptance of the HIV test;
* Forecast of hospital stay of more than twenty-four hours;
* Clinical and laboratory indication of RIPE;
* Conditions for puncture of venous access;

Exclusion Criteria:

* Brazilian indigenous people;
* Peo

Inclusion Criteria:

1. subjects were aged 18-80 years old;
2. a diagnosis of idiopathic or post-infective bronchiectasis was made;
3. patients had at least two exacerbations in the past year and were in a stable state for at least 4 weeks prior to the primary enrollment.

Exclusion Criteria:

Patie
